**Quaker** | Townsfolk Power | Limited
__Basics__
The Quaker selects a role and is informed when the last player with that role dies.
__Details__
The Quaker may immediately change their target once per phase, with 1 emergency change to be used whenever the Quaker wants to. 
If several players died at the same time the Quaker is not informed which of the players had their selected role.
If there are no players of the selected role, or if the last player with the selected role changes to a different role, the Quaker is not informed.
